  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1987040/extras/782c9e8f7261492ca721b0707c4380f9.avif?t=1713889206\" width=386 height=150 /></span><br><br>Jim is a new recruit in a spy organization. His country is threatened to be invaded by an army of robots. He will be sent on several missions to protect his homeland.<br><br>The game features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>10 different worlds<br></li><li>3 difficulty settings and list of objectives for each world<br></li><li>a jazzy/espionage/retro atmosphere in a modern world<br></li><li>a lifetime of around 5 hours</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1987040/extras/112f428745ae50fafac579029d3eb7c7.avif?t=1713889206\" width=386 height=150 /></span>",
